<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1" />
<title>ÌíçÏÑ†Í±∞Ïù∏ Îü¨ÎÑà ¬∑ ULTRA STABLE</title>
<style>
:root{ --page:#000; --ink:#0b1020; --card:#ffffff; }
*{box-sizing:border-box}
html,body{height:100%;margin:0;background:var(--page);color:var(--ink);font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Pretendard,Apple SD Gothic Neo,Noto Sans KR,sans-serif}
#app{min-height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.topbar,.bottombar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:8px 12px;background:#111;color:#fff}
.bottombar{justify-content:center}
.logo{font-weight:700}
.stage-wrap{position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;padding:10px}
canvas#game{width:min(96vw,1100px);height:auto;border-radius:14px;border:0;display:block;background:#9fd7ff}
/* HUD */
.hud{position:absolute;top:18px;left:18px;right:18px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;z-index:10}
.hud-left{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
.hud-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-weight:800}
.hud .score{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e1eaf4;padding:6px 10px;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
.hud .status{color:#334;font-weight:700;text-shadow:0 1px 0 #fff}
.inv-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.inv-icon{font-size:16px}
.inv-bar{position:relative;width:180px;height:10px;border:1px solid #eed27a;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(255,210,77,0.28);overflow:hidden}
.inv-bar > i{display:block;height:100%;background:#ffd24d;width:0%}
.overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(250,252,255,.92);backdrop-filter:blur(6px)}
.overlay.show{display:flex}
.card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid #e1eaf4;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 12px 32px rgba(40,60,100,.12);max-width:760px;width:min(94vw,760px);padding:20px}
.card h1,.card h2{margin-top:0}
.primary{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#5b8cff,#4b7ef8);border:none;color:#fff;font-weight:800;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:12px;cursor:pointer}
.primary:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
.lb{margin-top:14px}
.lb-list{margin:0 0 8px 0;padding-left:20px;max-height:180px;overflow:auto}
.name-entry{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;margin:10px 0}
.name-entry input{flex:1;border:1px solid #cfe0f7;border-radius:10px;padding:8px 10px}
.small{color:#667}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="app">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="logo">üéà ÌíçÏÑ†Í±∞Ïù∏ Îü¨ÎÑà ¬∑ ULTRA STABLE</div>
      <div class="small">Space/ÌÉ≠=Ï†êÌîÑ(ÌôÄÎìú=Í∞ÄÎ≥Ä) ¬∑ P=ÏùºÏãúÏ†ïÏßÄ ¬∑ R=Îã§Ïãú</div>
    </header>

    <div class="stage-wrap">
      <canvas id="game" width="1280" height="720" aria-label="Game Canvas"></canvas>

      <!-- HUD -->
      <div class="hud">
        <div class="hud-left">
          <div class="inv-row"><span class="inv-icon">ü¶ã Î¨¥Ï†Å</span><div class="inv-bar"><i id="invFill" style="width:0%"></i></div></div>
          <div class="status"><span id="stateTxt">READY</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hud-right">
          <div class="score">Ï†êÏàò <span id="scoreTxt">0</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="menu" class="overlay show">
        <div class="card">
          <h1>üéà ÌíçÏÑ†Í±∞Ïù∏ Îü¨ÎÑà</h1>
          <p>Ïä§ÌîÑÎùºÏù¥Ìä∏ Ï∫êÎ¶≠ÌÑ∞ + <b>ÌíçÏÑ† ÍΩÉ</b> Ïû•Ïï†Î¨º + <b>ÎÇòÎπÑ Î¨¥Ï†Å</b> Ìè¨Ìï®.</p>
          <button id="btnStart" class="primary">Í≤åÏûÑ ÏãúÏûë</button>
          <div class="lb">
            <h3>Î°úÏª¨ Î¶¨ÎçîÎ≥¥Îìú Top 10</h3>
            <ol id="lbList" class="lb-list"></ol>
            <div id="persistMsg" class="small"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="gameover" class="overlay">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Í≤åÏûÑ Ïò§Î≤Ñ</h2>
          <p>ÏµúÏ¢Ö Ï†êÏàò: <b id="finalScore">0</b></p>
          <div class="name-entry">
            <label for="playerName">Ïù¥Î¶Ñ(ÏµúÎåÄ 8Ïûê):</label>
            <input id="playerName" maxlength="8" placeholder="ÏùµÎ™Ö" />
            <button id="btnSaveScore">Ï†êÏàò Ï†ÄÏû•</button>
          </div>
          <div class="lb">
            <h3>Î¶¨ÎçîÎ≥¥Îìú Top 10</h3>
            <ol id="lbList2" class="lb-list"></ol>
            <div id="persistMsg2" class="small"></div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap">
            <button id="btnRestart" class="primary">Îã§Ïãú ÌïòÍ∏∞ (R)</button>
            <button id="btnMenu">Î©îÎâ¥Î°ú</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bottombar">
      <small style="color:#aaa">¬© 2025 ÌíçÏÑ†Í±∞Ïù∏ ÌîÑÎ°úÏ†ùÌä∏ ‚Äî Dino physics, sprites, invincibility & leaderboard</small>
    </footer>
  </div>

<script>
(function(){
  'use strict';
  const canvas = document.getElementById('game');
  const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');

  // Sprites (inline)
  const run1 = new Image(); run1.src = "data:image/png;base64,";
  const run2 = new Image(); run2.src = "data:image/png;base64,";
  const jumpImg = new Image(); jumpImg.src = "data:image/png;base64,";
  const flower = [new Image(), new Image()]; flower[0].src="data:image/png;base64,"; flower[1].src="data:image/png;base64,";
  const butterfly = new Image(); butterfly.src="data:image/png;base64,";

  // HUD Elements
  const elScore = document.getElementById('scoreTxt');
  const elState = document.getElementById('stateTxt');
  const invFill = document.getElementById('invFill');

  // Menu/Overlays
  const elMenu = document.getElementById('menu');
  const elGameOver = document.getElementById('gameover');
  const btnStart = document.getElementById('btnStart');
  const btnRestart = document.getElementById('btnRestart');
  const btnMenu = document.getElementById('btnMenu');
  const elFinal = document.getElementById('finalScore');
  const elLb1 = document.getElementById('lbList');
  const elLb2 = document.getElementById('lbList2');
  const elName = document.getElementById('playerName');
  const btnSave = document.getElementById('btnSaveScore');
  const persistMsg = document.getElementById('persistMsg');
  const persistMsg2 = document.getElementById('persistMsg2');

  // Leaderboard
  const LB_KEY = 'balloon-giant-lb-v4';
  let memoryLB = []; let storageOK = true;
  try { localStorage.setItem('__test','1'); localStorage.removeItem('__test'); } catch(e){ storageOK=false; }
  function loadLB(){ if(!storageOK) return memoryLB; try{ const raw=localStorage.getItem(LB_KEY); if(!raw) return []; const arr=JSON.parse(raw); if(Array.isArray(arr)) return arr; }catch(e){} return []; }
  function saveLB(arr){ if(!storageOK){ memoryLB = arr.slice(0,10); return; } try{ localStorage.setItem(LB_KEY, JSON.stringify(arr.slice(0,10))); }catch(e){} }
  function addLB(name,score){ const arr=loadLB(); arr.push({name:(name||'ÏùµÎ™Ö').slice(0,8),score:Math.floor(score),at:Date.now()}); arr.sort((a,b)=>b.score-a.score); saveLB(arr); }
  function renderLB(ol){ const arr=loadLB(); ol.innerHTML=''; arr.slice(0,10).forEach((r,i)=>{ const li=document.createElement('li'); const d=new Date(r.at); li.textContent=`${i+1}. ${r.name} ‚Äî ${r.score}Ï†ê (${d.getMonth()+1}/${d.getDate()})`; ol.appendChild(li); }); }
  function updatePersistMsg(){ const t=storageOK?'Ï†ÄÏû• ÏúÑÏπò: Ïù¥ Î∏åÎùºÏö∞Ï†Ä(localStorage)':'Ï†ÄÏû• ÏúÑÏπò: ÏÑ∏ÏÖò Î©îÎ™®Î¶¨(ÌÉ≠ Îã´ÏúºÎ©¥ Ï¥àÍ∏∞Ìôî)'; persistMsg.textContent=t; persistMsg2.textContent=t; }

  // Landscape
  const BASE_W=1280, BASE_H=720; const GROUND_Y=BASE_H-120;

  // World
  let state='menu', last=0, acc=0, STEP=1000/60;
  let score=0, speed=8, spawnTimer=0;
  const obstacles=[]; const items=[]; let itemTimer=0;

  // Clouds (light, top band only)
  const cloudsFar=[], cloudsNear=[];
  function initClouds(){
    cloudsFar.length=0; cloudsNear.length=0;
    for(let i=0;i<3;i++){
      const w=150+Math.random()*120, h=50+Math.random()*20;
      cloudsFar.push({x:Math.random()*BASE_W, y:30+Math.random()*80, w, h, v:0.10+Math.random()*0.06, a:0.65});
    }
    for(let i=0;i<2;i++){
      const w=180+Math.random()*140, h=60+Math.random()*24;
      cloudsNear.push({x:Math.random()*BASE_W, y:50+Math.random()*90, w, h, v:0.18+Math.random()*0.08, a:0.85});
    }
  }
  function updateClouds(dt){
    const wrapFar=c=>{ if(c.x + c.w < -60){ c.x = BASE_W + Math.random()*200; c.y = 30 + Math.random()*80; } };
    const wrapNear=c=>{ if(c.x + c.w < -60){ c.x = BASE_W + Math.random()*220; c.y = 50 + Math.random()*90; } };
    for(const c of cloudsFar){ c.x -= c.v * (1 + (speed-8)*0.01); wrapFar(c); }
    for(const c of cloudsNear){ c.x -= c.v * (1 + (speed-8)*0.015); wrapNear(c); }
  }
  function drawCloud(c){
    const cx=c.x, cy=c.y, w=c.w, h=c.h, r=h*0.5;
    ctx.save(); ctx.globalAlpha=c.a; ctx.fillStyle='#fff'; ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.arc(cx + w*0.15, cy + h*0.6, r*0.72, 0, Math.PI*2);
    ctx.arc(cx + w*0.35, cy + h*0.45, r*0.88, 0, Math.PI*2);
    ctx.arc(cx + w*0.60, cy + h*0.50, r*0.95, 0, Math.PI*2);
    ctx.arc(cx + w*0.80, cy + h*0.65, r*0.70, 0, Math.PI*2);
    ctx.closePath(); ctx.fill(); ctx.restore();
  }

  // Input
  let wantJump=false, holding=false, holdMs=0;
  function isTyping(){ const ae=document.activeElement; return !!ae && (ae.tagName==='INPUT'||ae.tagName==='TEXTAREA'||ae.isContentEditable); }
  window.addEventListener('keydown',e=>{
    if(isTyping()){ if(e.code==='Enter' && state==='gameover'){ e.preventDefault(); saveScore(); } return; }
    if(e.repeat) return;
    if(e.code==='Space'||e.code==='ArrowUp'){ e.preventDefault(); holding=true; requestJump(); }
    if(e.code==='KeyP'){ togglePause(); }
    if(e.code==='KeyR'){ if(state==='gameover'){ reset(); play(); } }
  });
  window.addEventListener('keyup',e=>{ if(isTyping()) return; if(e.code==='Space'||e.code==='ArrowUp') holding=false; });
  canvas.addEventListener('pointerdown',()=>{ if(isTyping()) return; holding=true; requestJump(); });
  canvas.addEventListener('pointerup',()=>{ if(isTyping()) return; holding=false; });

  btnStart.onclick=()=>{ reset(); play(); };
  btnRestart.onclick=()=>{ reset(); play(); };
  btnMenu.onclick=()=>{ show(elMenu,true); show(elGameOver,false); state='menu'; elState.textContent='READY'; renderLB(elLb1); };
  btnSave.onclick=()=> saveScore();

  function requestJump(){ if(state!=='playing') return; wantJump=true; }
  function togglePause(){ if(state==='playing'){ state='paused'; show(elMenu,true); elState.textContent='PAUSED'; } else if(state==='paused'){ show(elMenu,false); state='playing'; elState.textContent='RUN!'; } }
  function show(el,v){ el.classList.toggle('show', !!v); }

  // Helpers
  class Rect{ constructor(x,y,w,h){ this.x=x; this.y=y; this.w=w; this.h=h; } }
  function intersects(a,b){ return !(a.x>b.x+b.w || a.x+a.w<b.x || a.y>b.y+b.h || a.y+a.h<b.y); }
  function fitCanvas(){ const dpr=Math.min(2,window.devicePixelRatio||1); canvas.width=BASE_W*dpr; canvas.height=BASE_H*dpr; ctx.setTransform(dpr,0,0,dpr,0,0); }
  window.addEventListener('resize', fitCanvas);

  // Player
  const player = {
    x:160, y:GROUND_Y-130, w:120, h:130,
    vy:0, onGround:true, animFrame:0, animTimer:0, inv:0,
    jump(){ if(this.onGround){ this.vy=-20; holdMs=0; this.onGround=false; } },
    update(dt){
      if(!this.onGround && holding && holdMs<180){ this.vy+=0.6; holdMs+=dt; } else { this.vy+=1.0; }
      this.y+=this.vy;
      if(this.y+this.h>=GROUND_Y){ this.y=GROUND_Y-this.h; this.vy=0; this.onGround=true; } else { this.onGround=false; }
      if(this.onGround){ this.animTimer+=dt; if(this.animTimer>100){ this.animFrame^=1; this.animTimer=0; } } else { this.animTimer=0; }
      if(this.inv>0) this.inv-=dt;
    },
    aabb(){ return new Rect(this.x+18, this.y+16, this.w-36, this.h-28); },
    draw(){
      ctx.save(); ctx.globalAlpha=0.16; ctx.fillStyle='#0b1020';
      ctx.beginPath(); ctx.ellipse(this.x+this.w*0.5, GROUND_Y+8, 58, 12, 0, 0, Math.PI*2); ctx.fill(); ctx.restore();
      const spr = this.onGround ? (this.animFrame===0 ? run1 : run2) : jumpImg;
      if(spr.complete) ctx.drawImage(spr, this.x, this.y, this.w, this.h);
    }
  };

  // Obstacles (flowers)
  function spawnObstacle(){
    const idx = Math.random()<0.5 ? 0 : 1;
    const aspect=0.56; const h= Math.random()*40+60; const w=Math.max(28,h*aspect);
    const insetX=w*0.15, insetY=h*0.10;
    obstacles.push({ x:BASE_W+40, y:GROUND_Y-h, w, h, img:idx, hitInsetX:insetX, hitInsetY:insetY });
    if(Math.random()<0.18){
      const h2=Math.random()*34+58, w2=Math.max(26,h2*aspect);
      obstacles.push({ x:BASE_W+40+(Math.random()*80+240), y:GROUND_Y-h2, w:w2, h:h2, img:1-idx, hitInsetX:w2*0.15, hitInsetY:h2*0.10 });
    }
  }
  function drawObstacle(o){ const img=flower[o.img]; if(img && img.complete) ctx.drawImage(img,o.x,o.y,o.w,o.h); else { ctx.fillStyle='#44cc7a'; ctx.fillRect(o.x,o.y,o.w,o.h); } }

  // Items (butterfly invincibility)
  function spawnButterfly(){ const h=64,w=84; const baseY=GROUND_Y-(140+Math.random()*120); items.push({x:BASE_W+40,y:baseY,baseY:baseY,w,h,phase:Math.random()*6.28}); }
  function drawButterfly(it){ if(butterfly && butterfly.complete) ctx.drawImage(butterfly,it.x,it.y,it.w,it.h); else { ctx.fillStyle='#ffd24d'; ctx.fillRect(it.x,it.y,it.w,it.h); } }

  // Game flow
  function reset(){ show(elMenu,false); show(elGameOver,false); state='playing'; elState.textContent='RUN!'; score=0; speed=8; spawnTimer=0; itemTimer=0; obstacles.length=0; items.length=0; player.x=160; player.y=GROUND_Y-player.h; player.vy=0; player.onGround=true; player.animFrame=0; player.animTimer=0; player.inv=0; invFill.style.width='0%'; }
  function play(){}
  function gameover(){ state='gameover'; elFinal.textContent=Math.floor(score); show(elGameOver,true); elName.focus(); renderLB(elLb2); }

  function saveScore(){ if(state!=='gameover') return; addLB(elName.value.trim()||'ÏùµÎ™Ö', score); elName.value=''; renderLB(elLb2); renderLB(elLb1); }

  // Loop
  function loop(t){ if(!last) last=t; const dt=t-last; last=t; acc+=dt; while(acc>=STEP){ tick(STEP); acc-=STEP; } draw(); requestAnimationFrame(loop); }

  function tick(dt){
    if(state!=='playing') return;
    score += dt*0.03;
    speed = Math.min(16, speed + 0.00015*dt);

    // spawn obstacles
    spawnTimer -= dt;
    if(spawnTimer<=0){
      spawnObstacle();
      const base = Math.random()*800 + 1600;
      const denom = 1 + (speed-8)*0.04;
      spawnTimer = Math.max(1100, base/denom);
    }

    // spawn items
    itemTimer -= dt;
    if(itemTimer<=0){ spawnButterfly(); itemTimer = Math.random()*6000 + 8000; }

    if(wantJump){ player.jump(); wantJump=false; }
    player.update(dt);

    // update clouds
    updateClouds(dt);

    // items update & collect
    for(const it of items){ it.phase += dt*0.006; it.y = it.baseY + Math.sin(it.phase)*10; it.x -= speed*0.9; if(it.x+it.w<-20) it.dead=true; }
    const pboxI = player.aabb();
    for(const it of items){ const hit={x:it.x+it.w*0.2,y:it.y+it.h*0.2,w:it.w*0.6,h:it.h*0.6}; if(!(pboxI.x>hit.x+hit.w||pboxI.x+pboxI.w<hit.x||pboxI.y>hit.y+hit.h||pboxI.y+pboxI.h<hit.y)){ it.dead=true; player.inv=Math.max(player.inv,3500); score+=200; } }
    for(let i=items.length-1;i>=0;i--){ if(items[i].dead) items.splice(i,1); }

    // obstacles move/collide
    const pbox = player.aabb();
    for(const o of obstacles){
      o.x -= speed; if(o.x+o.w<-30) o.dead=true;
      const hit = new Rect(o.x+(o.hitInsetX||0), o.y+(o.hitInsetY||0), o.w-2*(o.hitInsetX||0), o.h-2*(o.hitInsetY||0));
      if(player.inv>0 ? false : intersects(pbox, hit)) gameover();
    }
    for(let i=obstacles.length-1;i>=0;i--){ if(obstacles[i].dead) obstacles.splice(i,1); }

    // HUD updates
    elScore.textContent = Math.floor(score);
    const invPct = Math.max(0, Math.min(1, player.inv/3500));
    invFill.style.width = (invPct*100).toFixed(1)+'%';
  }

  // Render
  function draw(){
    ctx.clearRect(0,0,BASE_W,BASE_H);
    // sky gradient
    const grd=ctx.createLinearGradient(0,0,0,BASE_H); grd.addColorStop(0,'#66b9ff'); grd.addColorStop(1,'#a6dcff'); ctx.fillStyle=grd; ctx.fillRect(0,0,BASE_W,BASE_H);
    // clouds
    for(const c of cloudsFar) drawCloud(c);
    for(const c of cloudsNear) drawCloud(c);
    // ground
    ctx.fillStyle='#6fdc6f'; ctx.fillRect(0, GROUND_Y, BASE_W, BASE_H-GROUND_Y);
    ctx.fillStyle='rgba(0,0,0,0.08)';
    for(let x=0;x<BASE_W;x+=22){ ctx.fillRect(x, GROUND_Y-2, 16, 2); ctx.fillRect(x+6, GROUND_Y+10, 12, 2); ctx.fillRect(x+12, GROUND_Y+20, 10, 2); }
    // objects
    for(const o of obstacles) drawObstacle(o);
    for(const it of items) drawButterfly(it);
    // player
    player.draw();
  }

  // Boot
  function boot(){ const dpr=Math.min(2,window.devicePixelRatio||1); canvas.width=BASE_W*dpr; canvas.height=BASE_H*dpr; ctx.setTransform(dpr,0,0,dpr,0,0); initClouds(); renderLB(elLb1); updatePersistMsg(); requestAnimationFrame(loop); }
  boot();

  // Leaderboard rendering on menu
  function renderLB(ol){ const arr=loadLB(); ol.innerHTML=''; arr.slice(0,10).forEach((r,i)=>{ const li=document.createElement('li'); const d=new Date(r.at); li.textContent=(i+1)+'. '+r.name+' ‚Äî '+r.score+'Ï†ê ('+(d.getMonth()+1)+'/'+d.getDate()+')'; ol.appendChild(li); }); }
  function updatePersistMsg(){ const t=storageOK?'Ï†ÄÏû• ÏúÑÏπò: Ïù¥ Î∏åÎùºÏö∞Ï†Ä(localStorage)':'Ï†ÄÏû• ÏúÑÏπò: ÏÑ∏ÏÖò Î©îÎ™®Î¶¨(ÌÉ≠ Îã´ÏúºÎ©¥ Ï¥àÍ∏∞Ìôî)'; persistMsg.textContent=t; persistMsg2.textContent=t; }

})();
</script>
</body>
</html>
